messages.content: ComfyUI-Openpose-Editor-Plus is an extension of ComfyUI that is expected to add the functions of background reference and imported poses on the basis of editing character actions.
What additional features are planned for ComfyUI-Openpose-Editor-Plus?
The planned additional features for ComfyUI-Openpose-Editor-Plus include background reference and imported poses.
The developer is currently busy and unsure when ComfyUI-Openpose-Editor-Plus will be completed.
What is the purpose of adding background reference and imported poses in ComfyUI-Openpose-Editor-Plus?
The purpose of adding background reference and imported poses in ComfyUI-Openpose-Editor-Plus is to enhance the editing of character actions.
Who is the developer of ComfyUI-Openpose-Editor-Plus?
The developer of ComfyUI-Openpose-Editor-Plus is whmc76 on GitHub.
Is there any visual representation of ComfyUI-Openpose-Editor-Plus?
Yes, there is an image asset provided in the GitHub repository that visually represents ComfyUI-Openpose-Editor-Plus.
Where can one find more information about ComfyUI-Openpose-Editor-Plus?
More information about ComfyUI-Openpose-Editor-Plus can be found on the GitHub repository of whmc76.
